Installation:

    rm -rf ~/.vim

    git clone git://github.com/scottyangx24/dotvim.git ~/.vim
    or
    git clone https://github.com/scottyangx24/dotvim.git ~/.vim
    

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

get vundle

    mkdir bundle
    cd bundle
    git clone https://github.com/gmarik/vundle.git ~/.vim/bundle/vundle

